opportunities within this market as having a proven need and an expressed desire for our robotic solution.</p>            </div>        </div>        <div class="row">            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">                <div class="row">                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">                        <div class="do-box text-center">                            <i class="lnr lnr-inbox"></i>                            <h3>TCM clinics</h3>                            <p>This group has identified a need for affordable supply of massage therapists/ robots that allow them to provide effective treatment at low cost. Medical massage robots allow TCM clinics to expand despite the shortage of manpower and rising foreign worker levy and quota. With the deployment of the robots, the clinic can reduce the manpower cost and generate more profits in the long run. Moreover, all TCM physicians have received letter from Singapore Police Force which informs us that medical massage can only be provided by registered physician only (therapists are not allowed). The strict law enforcement will further increase the need of our medical massage robots.</p>                        </div>                    </div>                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">                        <div class="do-box bg-color text-center">                            <i class="lnr lnr-cog"></i>                            <h3>TCM physicians</h3>                            <p>Currently, TCM physicians bear extra responsibilities for whatever conduct done by the therapists in the clinic. The physician may be sued due to any damage caused by the massage therapist even though such action directly deviates from the physician's instruction. The legal fees could be hundreds of thousands of dollars and there is even a risk of getting censured or suspended. It is not uncommon that some therapists sometimes do not follow the instructions of the physicians entirely, especially when a less qualified non-medical personnel is recruited due to the desperate need for massage therapists in some clinics. If our robots are deployed, physicians can set the key massage parameters and execute their massage treatment plans easily and safely.</p>                        </div>                    </div>                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">                        <div class="do-box text-center">                            <i class="lnr lnr-leaf"></i>                            <h3>Massage Therapists</h3>                            <p>The utilization of massage robot does not mean the loss of jobs for local massage therapists. The robots can fulfill the labour shortage, but the therapists' knowledge and experiences are still valuable assets to TCM clinics. They can play a better role by upgrading to supervisors and sales persons. They can help the physicians to monitor and control the robots so that the physicians are freed from such work and focus on acupuncture and internal medicine.</p>                        </div>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div></section><!--======== end what we do =========--><!--======== about us =========--><section id="emma" class="about-us">    <div class="container-fluid">        <div class="row">            <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 p-l-r-0">                <div id="about" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">                    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">                        <div class="item active">                            <img src="images/about-us-2.jpg" width="100%" alt="" />                        </div>                        <div class="item">                            <img src="images/about-us-1.jpg" width="100%" alt="" />                        </div>                        <div class="item">                            <img src="images/about-us.jpg" width="100%" alt="" />                        </div>                    </div>                </div>            </div>            <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">                <div class="about-content">                    <h2 class="section-title">EMMA</h2>                    <p>EMMA - Quick, Easy and Reliable                        Traditional Medical Massage Robot. By developing EMMA, we aim to increase the productivity of TCM physicians and reduce the operational cost of TCM clinics.                        Through more scientific research and development, AITREAT works hard to make this ancient medical practice better understood and use it to preserve health and bring more happiness to mankind.</p>                    <p>The four function : PRECISION, SAFETY - PHYSICAL CONTACT,MULTIPLE THERAPY,INTELLIGENT LEARNING</p>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div></section><!--======== end about us =========--><!--======== our service =========--><section id="team" class="our-service">    <div class="container">        <div class="row">            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center">                <p class="small-tag">What make us strong</p>                <h2 class="section-title">Our Team</h2>                <div class="border"><span class="border-l-r"><i class="lnr lnr-diamond"></i></span></div>                <p class="section-para">The Board is responsible for the group’s strategy and for overseeing the group’s performance, and delegates day-to-day responsibility to executive management. But there are a number of matters reserved to the Board.</p>            </div>        </div>        {{--<div class="row">--}}            {{--<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">--}}                {{--<div class="four-slide">--}}                    {{--<div class="single-slide"><img src="images/service-1.jpg" alt="">--}}                        {{--<div class="service-overflow text-center">--}}         